">\u003Cdiv class=\"attribution\">Text encoding: Marta Fogagnolo\u003C/div>\u003Cdiv id=\"edition-interpretive\" lang=\"grc\">  \u003Cdiv class=\"textpart\" lang=\"grc\">\u003Cspan class=\"ab\" id=\"div-interpretive\">  \u003Ca id=\"al0-interpretive\">\u003C!--0-->\u003C/a>[\u003Cspan dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---\u003C/span>] \u003Cbr id=\"al1-interpretive\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">1\u003C/span>[\u003Cspan dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---\u003C/span>  \u003Cspan data-text=\"ἐποίησε\">ἐ]ποίησ̣[ε\u003C/span>  \u003Cspan dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---\u003C/span>] \u003Cbr id=\"al2-interpretive\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">2\u003C/span>[\u003Cspan dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---\u003C/span> ε]ὐσεβ\u003Cspan dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">.\u003C/span> [\u003Cspan dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---\u003C/span>] \u003Cbr id=\"al3-interpretive\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">3\u003C/span>[\u003Cspan dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---\u003C/span>  \u003Cspan data-text=\"ἒζησε\">ἒ]ζησε\u003C/span>  \u003Cspan data-text=\"ἒτη\">ἒ[τη\u003C/span>  \u003Cspan dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---\u003C/span>] \u003C/span>\u003C/div>  \u003Cp class=\"miniapp\">\u003C/p>\u003C/div>\u003Cdiv class=\"attribution\">Text encoding: Marta Fogagnolo\u003C/div>\u003Cdiv id=\"edition-diplomatic\" lang=\"grc\">\u003Cdiv class=\"textpart\" lang=\"grc\">\u003Cspan class=\"ab\" id=\"div-diplomatic\">\u003Ca id=\"al0-diplomatic\">\u003C!--0-->\u003C/a>[\u003Cspan dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---\u003C/span>]\u003Cbr id=\"al1-diplomatic\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">1\u003C/span>[\u003Cspan dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---\u003C/span>\u003Cspan data-text=\"ἐποίησε\">.]ΠΟΙΗ.[.\u003C/span>\u003Cspan dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---\u003C/span>]\u003Cbr id=\"al2-diplomatic\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">2\u003C/span>[\u003Cspan dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---\u003C/span>.]ΥΣΕΒ\u003Cspan dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">·\u003C/span>[\u003Cspan dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---\u003C/span>]\u003Cbr id=\"al3-diplomatic\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">3\u003C/span>[\u003Cspan dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---\u003C/span>\u003Cspan data-text=\"ἒζησε\">.]ΖΗΣΕ\u003C/span>\u003Cspan data-text=\"ἒτη\">Ε[..\u003C/span>\u003Cspan dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---\u003C/span>]\u003C/span>\u003C/div>\u003Cp class=\"miniapp\">\u003C/p>\u003C/div>\u003C/div>  \u003Cdiv id=\"facsimile-images\">\u003Ch2>Facsimile Images\u003C/h2>\u003Ca href=\"ISic001335_tiled.tif\">\u003Cimg title=\"I.Sicily with the permission of the Assessorato Regionale dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana - Dipartimento dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana\" src=\"ISic001335_tiled-thumb.tif\">\u003C/a>\u003Ca href=\"ISic001335.jpg\">\u003Cimg title=\"I.Sicily with the permission of the Assessorato Regionale dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana - Dipartimento dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana\" src=\"ISic001335-thumb.jpg\">\u003C/a>\u003C/div>  \u003Cdiv id=\"apparatus\">\u003Ch4>Apparatus criticus\u003C/h4>\u003Cul>\u003Cli>\u003Cspan>\u003Cspan>Text based on photographs\u003C/span>\u003C/span>; \u003C/li>\u003Cli>\u003Cspan class=\"line 1\">line.1: \u003Cspan>Kirchhoff: ἐ]ποίησ[αν; Korhonen: ἐ]ποίησ[ε\u003C/span>\u003C/span>\u003Cbr>\u003C/li>\u003Cli>\u003Cspan class=\"line 2\">line.2: \u003Cspan>Kirchhoff: ε]ὐσεβ[εῖς; Kaibel: ἐ]υσεβ[εστατ---\u003C/span>\u003C/span>\u003C/li>\u003C/ul>\u003C/div>  \u003Cdiv id=\"translation\">\u003Ch2>English translation\u003C/h2>\u003Cp class=\"translation-author\">\u003Ca href=\"https://orcid.org/0000-0001-5187-5163\">Marta Fogagnolo\u003C/a>\u003C/p>  \u003Cp>--- made --- lived for --- years ---\u003C/p>  \u003C/div>  \u003Cdiv id=\"translation\">\u003Ch2>Italian translation\u003C/h2>\u003Cp class=\"translation-author\">\u003Ca href=\"https://orcid.org/0000-0001-5187-5163\">Marta Fogagnolo\u003C/a>\u003C/p>  \u003Cp>--- fece --- visse --- anni ---\u003C/p>  \u003C/div>  \u003Cdiv id=\"commentary\">\u003Ch2>commentary\u003C/h2>  \u003Cp>The epitaph is fragmentary: Korhonen (2004: 243) suggested two possible formulae, the first with the name of the deceased in dative followed by \u003Cspan class=\"lang\" lang=\"grc\">[ἐ]ποίησ[εν υἱὸς ε]υσεβή[ς]\u003C/span> (see also IG 14.527 = \u003Ca href=\"http://sicily.classics.ox.ac.uk/inscription/ISic001346\" target=\"_blank\">ISic001346\u003C/a>), the second with the name of the dedicant in nominative and the dative of the deceased, not named (e.g. \u003Cspan class=\"lang\" lang=\"grc\">[ὁ δεῖνα ἐ]ποίησ[εν υἱῷ ε]ὐσεβ&lt;ε&gt;ῖ\u003C/span>, \u003Cspan class=\"lang\" lang=\"grc\">[ὃς ἔ]ζησε ἔ[τη κτλ.]\u003C/span>). The Korhonen rejects Kaibel’s reading \u003Cspan class=\"lang\" lang=\"grc\">ε]ὐσεβ[εστάτ\u003C/span> because he reads a vertical stroke after \u003Cspan class=\"lang\" lang=\"grc\">Β\u003C/span>, which could only have been an \u003Cspan class=\"lang\" lang=\"grc\">Η\u003C/span> or a \u003Cspan class=\"lang\" lang=\"grc\">Ι\u003C/span>. \u003Cspan class=\"lang\" lang=\"grc\">ε]ὐσεβ[\u003C/span> at l. 2 could also be not a form of the adjective but a proper name, such as \u003Cspan class=\"lang\" lang=\"grc\">Εὐσεβία\u003C/span> or \u003Cspan class=\"lang\" lang=\"grc\">Εὐσέβιος\u003C/span> (LGPN 3A: 176). However, since we are not sure how much space is missing on the left and right, it is also possible that the deceased had a different degree of kinship (\u003Cspan class=\"lang\" lang=\"grc\">[ὁ δεῖνα ἐ]ποίησ[εν συμβίῳ ε]ὐσεβῖ\u003C/span>, see also IG 14.492 = \u003Ca href=\"http://sicily.classics.ox.ac.uk/inscription/ISic001314\" target=\"_blank\">ISic001314\u003C/a> or IG 14.495 = \u003Ca href=\"http://sicily.classics.ox.ac.uk/inscription/ISic001317\" target=\"_blank\">ISic001317\u003C/a>).\u003C/p>  \u003C/div>  \u003Cdiv id=\"bibliography\">\u003Ch2>bibliography\u003C/h2>  \u003Cul>\u003Cli> Amico 1741 277 \u003Ca href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002186\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002186\u003C/a>\u003C/li>\u003Cli> Kirchhoff 1877 9507 \u003Ca href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001249\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001249\u003C/a>\u003C/li>\u003Cli> Kaibel 1890 \u003Ca href=\"https://clio.columbia.edu/catalog/6873760\" target=\"_blank\">515\u003C/a>  \u003Ca href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001072\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001072\u003C/a>\u003C/li>\u003Cli> Korhonen 2004 158 \u003Ca href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000028\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000028\u003C/a>\u003C/li>\u003C/ul>  \u003Cul>\u003Cli>\u003C/li>\u003C/ul>  \u003C/div>  \u003Cdiv id=\"handnote\">\u003Cp>Regular letters, Ε and Σ lunate.\u003C/p> Lines 1-3  17-20  Interlineation line 1 to 2  not recorded  \u003C/div>\u003Cdiv id=\"license\"> Licensed under a Creative Commons-Attribution 4.0 licence. \u003C/div>",[247,250,253,256,259,261,264,267,270],{"id":248,"html":249},"editions","\u003Cdiv class=\"attribution\">Text encoding: Marta Fogagnolo\u003C/div>\u003Cdiv id=\"edition-interpretive\" lang=\"grc\">  \u003Cdiv class=\"textpart\" lang=\"grc\">\u003Cspan class=\"ab\" id=\"div-interpretive\">  \u003Ca id=\"al0-interpretive\">\u003C!--0-->\u003C/a>[\u003Cspan dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---\u003C/span>] \u003Cbr id=\"al1-interpretive\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">1\u003C/span>[\u003Cspan dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---\u003C/span>  \u003Cspan data-text=\"ἐποίησε\">ἐ]ποίησ̣[ε\u003C/span>  \u003Cspan dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---\u003C/span>] \u003Cbr id=\"al2-interpretive\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">2\u003C/span>[\u003Cspan dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---\u003C/span> ε]ὐσεβ\u003Cspan dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">.\u003C/span> [\u003Cspan dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---\u003C/span>] \u003Cbr id=\"al3-interpretive\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">3\u003C/span>[\u003Cspan dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---\u003C/span>  \u003Cspan data-text=\"ἒζησε\">ἒ]ζησε\u003C/span>  \u003Cspan data-text=\"ἒτη\">ἒ[τη\u003C/span>  \u003Cspan dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---\u003C/span>] \u003C/span>\u003C/div>  \u003Cp class=\"miniapp\">\u003C/p>\u003C/div>\u003Cdiv class=\"attribution\">Text encoding: Marta Fogagnolo\u003C/div>\u003Cdiv id=\"edition-diplomatic\" lang=\"grc\">\u003Cdiv class=\"textpart\" lang=\"grc\">\u003Cspan class=\"ab\" id=\"div-diplomatic\">\u003Ca id=\"al0-diplomatic\">\u003C!--0-->\u003C/a>[\u003Cspan dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---\u003C/span>]\u003Cbr id=\"al1-diplomatic\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">1\u003C/span>[\u003Cspan dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---\u003C/span>\u003Cspan data-text=\"ἐποίησε\">.]ΠΟΙΗ.[.\u003C/span>\u003Cspan dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---\u003C/span>]\u003Cbr id=\"al2-diplomatic\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">2\u003C/span>[\u003Cspan dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---\u003C/span>.]ΥΣΕΒ\u003Cspan dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">·\u003C/span>[\u003Cspan dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---\u003C/span>]\u003Cbr id=\"al3-diplomatic\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">3\u003C/span>[\u003Cspan dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---\u003C/span>\u003Cspan data-text=\"ἒζησε\">.]ΖΗΣΕ\u003C/span>\u003Cspan data-text=\"ἒτη\">Ε[..\u003C/span>\u003Cspan dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---\u003C/span>]\u003C/span>\u003C/div>\u003Cp class=\"miniapp\">\u003C/p>\u003C/div>",{"id":251,"html":252},"facsimile-images","\u003Ch2>Facsimile Images\u003C/h2>\u003Ca href=\"ISic001335_tiled.tif\">\u003Cimg title=\"I.Sicily with the permission of the Assessorato Regionale dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana - Dipartimento dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana\" src=\"ISic001335_tiled-thumb.tif\">\u003C/a>\u003Ca href=\"ISic001335.jpg\">\u003Cimg title=\"I.Sicily with the permission of the Assessorato Regionale dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana - Dipartimento dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana\" src=\"ISic001335-thumb.jpg\">\u003C/a>",{"id":254,"html":255},"apparatus","\u003Ch4>Apparatus criticus\u003C/h4>\u003Cul>\u003Cli>\u003Cspan>\u003Cspan>Text based on photographs\u003C/span>\u003C/span>; \u003C/li>\u003Cli>\u003Cspan class=\"line 1\">line.1: \u003Cspan>Kirchhoff: ἐ]ποίησ[αν; Korhonen: ἐ]ποίησ[ε\u003C/span>\u003C/span>\u003Cbr>\u003C/li>\u003Cli>\u003Cspan class=\"line 2\">line.2: \u003Cspan>Kirchhoff: ε]ὐσεβ[εῖς; Kaibel: ἐ]υσεβ[εστατ---\u003C/span>\u003C/span>\u003C/li>\u003C/ul>",{"id":257,"html":258},"translation","\u003Ch2>English translation\u003C/h2>\u003Cp class=\"translation-author\">\u003Ca href=\"https://orcid.org/0000-0001-5187-5163\">Marta Fogagnolo\u003C/a>\u003C/p>  \u003Cp>--- made --- lived for --- years ---\u003C/p>  ",{"id":257,"html":260},"\u003Ch2>Italian translation\u003C/h2>\u003Cp class=\"translation-author\">\u003Ca href=\"https://orcid.org/0000-0001-5187-5163\">Marta Fogagnolo\u003C/a>\u003C/p>  \u003Cp>--- fece --- visse --- anni ---\u003C/p>  ",{"id":262,"html":263},"commentary","\u003Ch2>commentary\u003C/h2>  \u003Cp>The epitaph is fragmentary: Korhonen (2004: 243) suggested two possible formulae, the first with the name of the deceased in dative followed by \u003Cspan class=\"lang\" lang=\"grc\">[ἐ]ποίησ[εν υἱὸς ε]υσεβή[ς]\u003C/span> (see also IG 14.527 = \u003Ca href=\"http://sicily.classics.ox.ac.uk/inscription/ISic001346\" target=\"_blank\">ISic001346\u003C/a>), the second with the name of the dedicant in nominative and the dative of the deceased, not named (e.g. \u003Cspan class=\"lang\" lang=\"grc\">[ὁ δεῖνα ἐ]ποίησ[εν υἱῷ ε]ὐσεβ&lt;ε&gt;ῖ\u003C/span>, \u003Cspan class=\"lang\" lang=\"grc\">[ὃς ἔ]ζησε ἔ[τη κτλ.]\u003C/span>). The Korhonen rejects Kaibel’s reading \u003Cspan class=\"lang\" lang=\"grc\">ε]ὐσεβ[εστάτ\u003C/span> because he reads a vertical stroke after \u003Cspan class=\"lang\" lang=\"grc\">Β\u003C/span>, which could only have been an \u003Cspan class=\"lang\" lang=\"grc\">Η\u003C/span> or a \u003Cspan class=\"lang\" lang=\"grc\">Ι\u003C/span>. \u003Cspan class=\"lang\" lang=\"grc\">ε]ὐσεβ[\u003C/span> at l. 2 could also be not a form of the adjective but a proper name, such as \u003Cspan class=\"lang\" lang=\"grc\">Εὐσεβία\u003C/span> or \u003Cspan class=\"lang\" lang=\"grc\">Εὐσέβιος\u003C/span> (LGPN 3A: 176). However, since we are not sure how much space is missing on the left and right, it is also possible that the deceased had a different degree of kinship (\u003Cspan class=\"lang\" lang=\"grc\">[ὁ δεῖνα ἐ]ποίησ[εν συμβίῳ ε]ὐσεβῖ\u003C/span>, see also IG 14.492 = \u003Ca href=\"http://sicily.classics.ox.ac.uk/inscription/ISic001314\" target=\"_blank\">ISic001314\u003C/a> or IG 14.495 = \u003Ca href=\"http://sicily.classics.ox.ac.uk/inscription/ISic001317\" target=\"_blank\">ISic001317\u003C/a>).\u003C/p>  ",{"id":265,"html":266},"bibliography","\u003Ch2>bibliography\u003C/h2>  \u003Cul>\u003Cli> Amico 1741 277 \u003Ca href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002186\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002186\u003C/a>\u003C/li>\u003Cli> Kirchhoff 1877 9507 \u003Ca href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001249\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001249\u003C/a>\u003C/li>\u003Cli> Kaibel 1890 \u003Ca href=\"https://clio.columbia.edu/catalog/6873760\" target=\"_blank\">515\u003C/a>  \u003Ca href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001072\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001072\u003C/a>\u003C/li>\u003Cli> Korhonen 2004 158 \u003Ca href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000028\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000028\u003C/a>\u003C/li>\u003C/ul>  \u003Cul>\u003Cli>\u003C/li>\u003C/ul>  ",{"id":268,"html":269},"handnote","\u003Cp>Regular letters, Ε and Σ lunate.\u003C/p> Lines 1-3  17-20  Interlineation line 1 to 2  not recorded  ",{"id":271,"html":272},"license"," Licensed under a Creative Commons-Attribution 4.0 licence. ",[274,276,279,280],{"html":275},"Text encoding: Marta Fogagnolo",{"id":277,"lang":129,"html":278},"edition-interpretive","\u003Cdiv class=\"textpart\" lang=\"grc\">\u003Cspan class=\"ab\" id=\